      "writtenOn": "2019-12-06T23:34:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Makes sense. For the comment, I\u0027ll add something to try to clarify this:\n\n    Attempt stopped before completion, due to some external event\n    and not a failure of the CLs to pass all tests...",
